data.description: Beautiful Modern and Updated RANCH Home 4Bed 2.5 BA, OPEN Concept! Roommate Floorplan, a Bonus Flex/Office Room, Double OVEN in Kitchen!! Kitchen also features stone gray cabinets, granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and a large island. Kitchen overlooks dining area and family room with fireplace. Primary suite features a walk-in closet and private bath with tiled shower. Large Extended Back Patio, & Front Covered Porch. Located Near the AIRPORT and I-85. Gray paint throughout property. This Gently Lived-In Home Build in 2020 will Surly Please You with it's Unique and Charming floorplan. Don't Miss This Open concept Deauville Ranch Home Plan, located in Retreat at Sierra Estates Community.
